thread.title: My pet rocks | Russ

author: courier-journal.com
title: My pet rocks | Russ
text:
Name: Russ.
Age: 1 Year
Neighborhood: Jeffersontown
Owner: Zach Hamilton
In the owner's words: Russ is a year and a half old short hair Jack Russell. He is named after a former Louisville basketball player, Russ Smith. Russ is a big time Cards fan. Russ loves to go on walks, nap, and chew on his favorite toys. Russ is a crazy little man. He runs around the house all day and chases the cats, Oscar and Emmy. When he gets tired he loves to lay in your lap and sleep.
